FBIS3-15975 "drsov048_a_94023" FBIS-SOV-94-048 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Yeltsin Appoints Middle East Representative LD1103122994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0840 GMT 11 Mar 94 LD1103122994 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS] [Text] Moscow March 11 TASS -- The Russian president decreed to appoint Viktor Posuvalyuk, member of the Russian Foreign Ministry Collegium and director of the Middle East and Nothern Africa Department at the Russian Foreign Ministry, a special representative of the Russian Federation president on Middle East settlement.
